# Jeff-supplied raw artifacts — never commit (PII; use sanitized test fixtures only).
# Broad pattern prevents future PII additions anywhere under "From Jeff/" (greptile P1).
# NOTE: files ALREADY committed here remain in git history — a `git filter-repo` scrub
# is required and tracked separately (see spec 12 §14); this ignore does NOT resolve it.
From Jeff/*
!From Jeff/style-guide/
